<div id="review_2677545328" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/2677545328" />
    <a title="Catherine" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/71649212-catherine"><img alt="Catherine" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1547679424p2/71649212.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/2677545328?book_show_action=true">Feb 05, 2019</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Catherine" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Catherine" href="/user/show/71649212-catherine">Catherine</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2677545328" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer7505257643713487515">Impressive as it is that this has lasted so long and is such a thorough account of far-reaching travels, it&apos;s not a thrilling read. Lots of names; places and people, distances and details which don&apos;t make it a great narrative.</span>
  <span id="freeText7505257643713487515" style="display:none">Impressive as it is that this has lasted so long and is such a thorough account of far-reaching travels, it's not a thrilling read. Lots of names; places and people, distances and details which don't make it a great narrative.</span>
  <a data-text-id="7505257643713487515" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


